## Summary
This documentation page explains the Revenue LTV Chart in Amplitude, which helps track monetization progress for new users over time (up to 12 months). It details how to set up the chart using revenue events, apply segmentation, and choose metrics like Total Revenue, New Paying Users, ARPU, and ARPPU to analyze monetization effectiveness.

